{
  "texts": [
    "We categorize all questions into three scenarios based on the conditions of knowledge, and examine the impact of the planning approach on each scenario.",
    "Figure 5 shows the performance of various models in the three scenarios.",
    "Generally, as the richness of knowledge increases, the accuracy of each model improves.",
    "The ReAct and Reflexion models enhance the performance in situations of insufficient knowledge through employing multi-time retrieval and critic mechanisms.",
    "However, the improvement in scenarios of conflicting knowledge and complete knowledge is relatively marginal."
  ]
}